Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}聖天空戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要墜入愛河每個人都會變得如此孤單?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正擁抱著比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切必定都是為了讓我倆能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在用淚水來呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你早就給了我 最寶貴的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對幸運圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真教人不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對寨巴哈壓倒性的兵力…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們還是得守住這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同盟軍主力部隊抵達之前,無論如何都要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們切賽立歐軍,並不在乎犧牲性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但憑剩下的兵力,根本就無力回天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,只要法尼利亞王駕駛\N伊斯帕農的人型裝甲助陣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能夠使士氣大振
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您務必相助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一同奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我梵·法尼爾擔任前鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感激您了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我要拜託你們一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們將她送至阿斯多利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官立刻備妥船隻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我能幫上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你在我就會想要依賴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再將你的力量,用在戰爭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明擁有如此雄厚的兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何還不允許我等進擊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我等四魔軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打敗那群同盟軍的烏合之眾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多倫卡喀大人究竟在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經由命運引導
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女將落入我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對幸運圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久便能敔動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨讓人哀傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它會沖刷一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵的思念將你帶回蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你也回應了他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大概是頭一遭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕我的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵一定會歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裏有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比誰都來得重要的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭根本無法滿足什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本無法孕育出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在不斷消耗物資與人命罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個專門評斷物品價值的商人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然無法阻止這種只會摧毀一切的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一點都不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不像我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美到讓女神都會嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德萊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不是個配得上你的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然說這些?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭很快就會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無論哪一方獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲的都是民眾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟那些民眾一起重新再站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:06:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我還有這點用處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去當個商人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與民同在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是要成為配得上你的男人的最佳捷徑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不曉得我有沒有辦法等下去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會讓你的心向著我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我愛你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要幫助梵?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯,請你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才能讓光柱出現飛到寨巴哈去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去見多倫卡喀親自拜託他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他停止這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是個說得通的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說,讓你身陷危險的話,梵會難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多倫卡喀那裏就由我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與命運改變裝置共鳴的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會將光柱引導過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以會從比灣取回這個機械
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為這個緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來結束這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是去見多倫卡喀的話,弗肯會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他特有的體貼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為他一定能讓我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對,我總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著要找人來讓我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然等到德萊甸離去我才發現這點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞連,你早就注意到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜拉娜公主,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是現在聽到你的溫柔安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又會開始依賴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想成為你的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空騎士亞連·歇薩爾,即將出征迎敵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也將與蜜拉娜公主暫時告別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願海龍神桀齊亞庇佑你身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願你武運昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪蘭度大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上級命令我們與第三十二小隊一起進攻加爾佛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒參加這種大戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用決戰武器?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去根本就無法攻進敵軍陣營
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得一口氣開條路出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是戰場上還有眾多我方士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要他們好看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就好好體驗我巴斯蘭新武器的厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以待在這裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得梵大人不會再回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,梅露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達目標上空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投下武器的同時上升翻轉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們用了那個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上空出現閃光\N什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士官長,出現強光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本就不叫打仗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,是新武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑立歐艦隊,咒迪亞艦隊,蓋丁艦隊遭殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦受到衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的同盟軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然使出這種邪惡招數
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會放過你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個惡魔!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算將寨巴哈趕盡殺絕是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死了也要詛咒你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵…梵他很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去阻止這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵他現在很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你一定會來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你很可能會死在寨巴哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了不好的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的反作用正在侵蝕著我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對黑色翅膀就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色翅膀是證據?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得以性命來彌補自己\N與多倫卡喀狼狽為奸之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死的話,梵就真的孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想見到梵難過的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定能夠克服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨過我的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了另一個嶄新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會改變這種悲哀的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的人型裝甲在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.57,0:17:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就全都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的因子都集合到我身邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是命運改變裝置完整啟動的最佳時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如我所預料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所預料?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我操縱命運讓你帶幻之月少女過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:18:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟還要玩弄命運到什麼地步?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個蠢問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該瞭解我的真正想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,你也應該瞭解我的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來殺我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏只有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個怪物!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是改變命運的中樞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作用與反作用最強的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這樣就能結束戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋亞也能得到真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼老是發生這種事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是發生這種令人難過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敔動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊,你就與我一同觀賞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對幸運圈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了保護你而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:57.34,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月兒彼方藍色探照燈照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:05.79,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降臨的天使 你究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:13.42,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的門扉即將開啟　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:19.57,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過這令人興奮的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:21.93,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.94,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃燒般的神秘雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.78,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真無邪的笑容讓我傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:34.58,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深處的暗示只傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.59,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了無止盡的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的鼓動無法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:49.56,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想帶著你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:57.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:05.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:13.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:19.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:21.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.01,0:22:30.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:34.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:38.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:49.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい

